<section class="page-header">
  <h1>Our Story</h1>
  <p>How Sara Clothing came to be, and what we stand for.</p>
</section>

<section class="section about-story" data-reveal>
  <div class="about-story__image">
    <img src="<%= typeof story !== 'undefined' && story.image ? story.image : '/images/about/founder.jpg' %>" alt="Sara Clothing founder at work" width="600" height="700" loading="lazy">
  </div>
  <div class="about-story__content">
    <h2 class="section__heading">Where It Began</h2>
    <p>Sara Clothing started with a single question: why does considered, well-made clothing feel so hard to find? What began as a small collection shared with friends grew into a boutique built on the same principle — clothes that respect both the wearer and the craft.</p>
    <p>Every collection is designed in-house, fitted with care, and produced in small batches rather than mass runs. We would rather make fewer pieces well than many pieces carelessly.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section about-values" data-reveal>
  <h2 class="section__heading">What We Value</h2>
  <div class="values-grid">
    <div class="value-card">
      <h3>Craftsmanship</h3>
      <p>Every seam and finish is checked by hand before a piece leaves our workshop.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <h3>Honesty</h3>
      <p>What you see in our photos is what arrives at your door — no filters, no surprises.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <h3>Longevity</h3>
      <p>We design pieces meant to stay in your wardrobe for years, not seasons.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section about-cta" data-reveal>
  <h2 class="section__heading">See the Collection</h2>
  <p>Explore the pieces that carry our story forward.</p>
  <a href="/shop" class="btn btn--primary">Shop Now</a>
</section>
